{"id":15328,"date":"2024-07-02T16:39:18","date_gmt":"2024-07-02T09:39:18","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=15328"},"modified":"2024-07-02T16:39:44","modified_gmt":"2024-07-02T09:39:44","slug":"o-to-noi-tang-toc-lap-rap-truoc-tin-sap-giam-phi-truoc-ba","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/o-to-noi-tang-toc-lap-rap-truoc-tin-sap-giam-phi-truoc-ba\/","title":{"rendered":"\u00d4 t\u00f4 n\u1ed9i t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c l\u1eafp r\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin s\u1eafp gi\u1ea3m ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"detail__cnt-top\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"detail-cmain\">\n<div class=\"detail-content afcbc-body \" data-role=\"content\">\n<h2>\u00d4 t\u00f4 l\u1eafp r\u00e1p l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0 t\u0103ng s\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/h2>\n<p>B\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh kinh t\u1ebf &#8211; x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a T\u1ed5ng c\u1ee5c Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea cho th\u1ea5y, th\u00e1ng 6\/2024 v\u1eeba qua, c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t l\u1eafp r\u00e1p 27.200 xe, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 200 xe so v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"\u00d4 t\u00f4 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, l\u1eafp r\u00e1p t\u0103ng s\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u1ea2nh: HTC\" href=\"https:\/\/baogiaothong.mediacdn.vn\/603483875699699712\/2023\/12\/29\/nha-may-lap-rap-2-1703841740930157990180.jpeg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-fancybox=\"img-lightbox\"><img decoding=\"async\" id=\"img_665123260432912384\" class=\"lightbox-content\" title=\"\u00d4 t\u00f4 n\u1ed9i t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c l\u1eafp r\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin s\u1eafp gi\u1ea3m ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1- \u1ea2nh 1.\" src=\"https:\/\/baogiaothong.mediacdn.vn\/603483875699699712\/2023\/12\/29\/nha-may-lap-rap-2-1703841740930157990180.jpeg\" alt=\"\u00d4 t\u00f4 n\u1ed9i t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c l\u1eafp r\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin s\u1eafp gi\u1ea3m ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1- \u1ea2nh 1.\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-author=\"\" data-original=\"https:\/\/baogiaothong.mediacdn.vn\/603483875699699712\/2023\/12\/29\/nha-may-lap-rap-2-1703841740930157990180.jpeg\" data-adbro-processed=\"true\" \/><\/a><\/div><figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\n<p class=\"NLPlaceholderShow\" data-placeholder=\"Nh\u1eadp ch\u00fa th\u00edch \u1ea3nh\">\u00d4 t\u00f4 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, l\u1eafp r\u00e1p t\u0103ng s\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u1ea2nh: HTC<\/p>\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, th\u00e1ng 5\/2024, s\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u1eafp r\u00e1p th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh g\u1ea7n 1.000 xe. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y, c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111ang t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t l\u1eafp r\u00e1p sau khi c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m 50% l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1.<\/p>\n<p>B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00e1ng 5 t\u0103ng cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o. B\u01b0\u1edbc sang th\u00e1ng 6, s\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u0103ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eabn do s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 trong c\u1ea3 th\u00e1ng 6 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c \u00f4 t\u00f4 l\u1eafp r\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m 50% l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1.<\/p>\n<p>T\u00ednh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m, c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh kho\u1ea3ng 144.000 \u00f4 t\u00f4, v\u1eabn th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n kho\u1ea3ng 3,2% so v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3 n\u0103m 2023.<\/p>\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00f4 t\u00f4 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t l\u1eafp r\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f2n t\u0103ng cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh khi cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 6, B\u1ed9 T\u00e0i ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 th\u1ea3o Ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecbnh quy \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee9c thu l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 v\u1edbi \u00f4 t\u00f4 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, l\u1eafp r\u00e1p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode\"><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/o-to-noi-tang-toc-lap-rap-truoc-tin-sap-giam-phi-truoc-ba\/0r1a9998-copy\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-15329\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-15329\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/0R1A9998-copy-696x462.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1067\" height=\"708\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/0R1A9998-copy-696x462.jpg 696w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/0R1A9998-copy-501x333.jpg 501w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/0R1A9998-copy-480x320.jpg 480w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/0R1A9998-copy-768x510.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/0R1A9998-copy-1536x1020.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/0R1A9998-copy.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1067px) 100vw, 1067px\" \/><\/a><figcaption class=\"PhotoCMS_Caption\">\n<p class=\"NLPlaceholderShow\" data-placeholder=\"Nh\u1eadp ch\u00fa th\u00edch \u1ea3nh\">C\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t l\u1eafp r\u00e1p \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u0103ng doanh s\u1ed1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m 50% l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1<\/p>\n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<div><\/div>\n<div id=\"pos-13\"><\/div>\n<div><\/div>\n<h2>Xe n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1ee9t ph\u00e1 doanh s\u1ed1<\/h2>\n<p>Theo d\u1ef1 th\u1ea3o Ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 T\u00e0i ch\u00ednh, t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 1\/8\/2024 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft ng\u00e0y 31\/1\/2025, m\u1ee9c thu l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 b\u1eb1ng 50% m\u1ee9c thu quy \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i Ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 10\/2022 c\u1ee7a Ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c Ngh\u1ecb quy\u1ebft hi\u1ec7n h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a H\u0110ND ho\u1eb7c Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh hi\u1ec7n h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a UBND t\u1ec9nh, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 tr\u1ef1c thu\u1ed9c trung \u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c thu l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u0103n b\u1ea3n s\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed5i, b\u1ed5 sung, thay th\u1ebf (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3).<\/p>\n<p>T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 1\/2\/2025 tr\u1edf \u0111i, m\u1ee9c thu l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n theo m\u1ee9c c\u0169.<\/p>\n<p>C\u0169ng theo B\u1ed9 T\u00e0i ch\u00ednh, d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3m 50% m\u1ee9c thu l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u00f4 t\u00f4 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, l\u1eafp r\u00e1p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m thu NSNN v\u1ec1 l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 b\u00ecnh qu\u00e2n kho\u1ea3ng 867 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/th\u00e1ng (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3m theo Ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 41\/2023\/N\u0110-CP).<\/p>\n<p>T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 thu ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3m thu t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3m thu\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1\u00a0l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng 5.200 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng<\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3m 50% m\u1ee9c thu l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u00f4 t\u00f4 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, l\u1eafp r\u00e1p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i thu NSNN c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Lu\u1eadt NSNN, kho\u1ea3n thu l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 thu\u1ed9c ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/p>\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3m 50% m\u1ee9c thu l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u00f4 t\u00f4, s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t l\u1eafp r\u00e1p trong n\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u0103ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng xe \u00f4 t\u00f4 ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 v\u00e0 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd n\u00ean s\u1ed1 thu t\u1eeb l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1, thu\u1ebf TT\u0110B, thu\u1ebf GTGT c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng.<\/p>\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ed1 thu th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf t\u1eeb thu\u1ebf TT\u0110B v\u00e0 thu\u1ebf GTGT ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung \u1edf 8 \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u01a1i c\u00f3 c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ty s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, l\u1eafp r\u00e1p \u00f4 t\u00f4 trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u00f2n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3m thu ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y (\u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch Trung \u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea5p b\u00f9 kho\u1ea3n h\u1ee5t thu n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u00d4 t\u00f4 l\u1eafp r\u00e1p l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0 t\u0103ng s\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1ee3ng B\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh kinh t\u1ebf &#8211; x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a T\u1ed5ng c\u1ee5c Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea cho th\u1ea5y, th\u00e1ng 6\/2024 v\u1eeba qua, c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t l\u1eafp r\u00e1p 27.200 xe, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 200 xe so v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u00d4 [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":15329,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_words":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15328"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15328"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15328\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":15332,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15328\/revisions\/15332"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/15329"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=15328"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=15328"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=15328"},{"taxonomy":"yst_prominent_words","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/yst_prominent_words?post=15328"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}